summary: People keep asking "how did rooster teeth manage to get Michael b. Jordan in its new show" like it's really a mystery. Have you...
body:
People keep asking “how did rooster teeth manage to get Michael b. Jordan in its new show” like it’s really a mystery. Have you seen his Twitter? Any interviews he’s done? Michael B. Jordan is a nerd just like us and probably said yes like “you had me at mech anime”

My question is how did they get David Tennant?

summary: Well, here I am after watching the last episodes with the tenth doctor and I’m telling you they were painful to watch knowing...
body:
Doctor Who Breaks Hearts!

Well, here I am after watching the last episodes with the tenth doctor and I’m telling you they were painful to watch knowing that he will never come back. I’ve got that feeling when my throat started to hurt because I don’t want to cry but I couldn’t hold it back anymore especially when he said “I don’t wanna go.” In the end as the Ood said “This song is ending. But the story never ends.” I knew that this show is marvelous and it will never stop to impress me.

Goodbye Tenth Doctor. Goodbye David Tennant. You will be missed.
